title: Tom Segura Gives Stephen A New Leather Jacket
description:
Comedian and author Tom Segura stopped by to chat about his world tour and his new book, “I’d Like to Play Alone, Please.” Listen as he gifts Stephen a very expensive leather jacket that Netflix paid for!
